title: Romeo's Hesitant About Making This Drastic Change In His Life
description:
Moving out of your parents' home comes with a mixture of emotions. In Romeo's case, he's not as excited as he once was at the thought of moving out.
He thought his parents needed him, but he realizes he needs them more than he thought. Will this hold him back from moving out? We discuss.
